                <text>Section 70(1)(g) is amended by omitting <amend.in quote="1">; and, without limiting the generality of the foregoing, clauses specifying the duties and powers of trustees or statutory supervisors, as the case may be, and the obligations of issuers may be prescribed as clauses that are deemed to be contained in such deeds</amend.in>.</text>
