                <text>This section amends the Trustee Companies Act 1967.</text>
              </para>
            </subprov>
            <subprov skeleton="no">
              <label auto.number="no" denominator="yes">2</label>
              <para>
                <text>Section 7(2) is amended by repealing paragraph (m) and substituting the following paragraph:</text>
                <amend increment="1" quote="1">
                  <label-para quote="1" skeleton="no">
                    <label auto.number="no" denominator="yes" quote="1">m</label>
                    <para>
                      <text>statutory supervisor (as defined in the Retirement Villages Act 2003) in respect of a retirement village covered by the trustee company's licence under the Securities Trustees and Statutory Supervisors Act <changeable><citation jurisdiction="nz">2009</citation></changeable>:</text>
                    </para>
