                    <label auto.number="no" denominator="yes" quote="1">p</label>
                    <para>
                      <text>trustee, statutory supervisor, or unit trustee (as defined in the Securities Trustees and Statutory Supervisors Act <changeable><citation jurisdiction="nz">2009</citation></changeable>) in respect of a security covered by the trustee company's licence under that Act:</text>
